text: KOEG (88.3 FM) in Walters is a radio station broadcasting a Catholic religious format. The station is owned by Blessed Sacrament Catholic Church Of Lawton, Oklahoma. ==History== This station was assigned call sign KOEG on September 4, 2009. ==References== ==External links== * * http://okcr.org/ OEG Category:Radio stations established in 2009 Category:Religious radio stations in the United States OEG
title: KOEG
